Package: SpatialTE
Type: Package
Title: Isoform-Level Quantification for Spatial and Single-Cell
        Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Puwen", "Tan", email = "hmutpw@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: EM-based isoform quantification for FFPE spatial transcriptomics
    and single-cell RNA-seq data. Integrates long-read bulk RNA-seq as a
    Dirichlet prior to guide spot/cell-level isoform estimation. Supports
    STAR toTranscriptome BAM input, FFPE-corrected effective length estimation,
    equivalence class compression, and spatial prior smoothing. Compatible with
    SpatialExperiment, SingleCellExperiment, Seurat, and downstream tools.
    Designed as a companion to the IsoEM package for TE-enriched isoform
    quantification workflows.
